OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Ffine end to the day with plenty of
OL,7,Fevening sunshine. Staying dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells, some
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud and light winds. Some
OL,10,Fmist and fog may develop in prone
OL,11,Fspots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FContinuing largely fine, dry
OL,14,Fand settled, however skies turning a
OL,15,Flittle hazy at times. Still feeling
OL,16,Frather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
