OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry over the next few days
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fsunny spells. A few showers are
OL,9,Fpossible where the cloud thickens.
OL,10,FRemaining warm.
